## Troubleshooting

### Database locked error
- Close all file explorers viewing the folder
- Restart the application

### Data not saving
- Check file permissions on project directory
- Ensure DatabaseManager.initialize() was called
- Check console for SQL error messages

### Slow queries
- Use refresh() sparingly
- Cache results in ObservableList between queries
- Consider batching inserts for bulk operations
